  <brief_title>Clinical Trial on Onychomycosis With P-3058 Nail Solution in Pediatric Population</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multicentre, Open Label Study to Assess the Tolerability of P-3058 Nail Solution in Paediatric Patients Affected by Mild-to-moderate Onychomycosis</official_title>
