  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pediatric patients affected by mild-to-moderate distal subungual onychomycosis (DSO) or
      affected by white superficial onychomycosis (WSO), due to dermatophytes, will be treated
      topically with P-3058 nail solution according to the appropriate treatment schedule.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
